                <h1>What is OpenAI? Understanding AI for Everyone</h1>
                <p>OpenAI is an artificial intelligence research organization aimed at ensuring that AI benefits all of humanity. Founded in December 2015, it focuses on developing advanced AI technologies and models like GPT-3, fostering safety, and promoting collaborative AI advancements. OpenAI's mission is to create beneficial and accessible AI for everyone.</p>
